data.description: Have you been searching for the perfect starter home or have the kids all moved out and you want something as low maintenance as possible?  Say less!  This beautifully renovated home in the highly sought after community of Crowfield Plantation is ready for new owners!The HVAC was just replaced last month and the owners also installed a new deck off the back porch AND added gutters!  Wow!!  The roof is also only a couple years old so you are looking at little to no big ticket items needing replaced anytime soon!!  Incredible! The owner's suite is located downstairs right off the living room and has its own walk in closet and ensuite bathroom.  Upstairs you will find the 2 additional bedrooms with another full bathroom!  This home is is in a quiet cul-de-sac with lots of mature treesand wildlife.
